nt":1},{"word":"town","count":1},{"word":"sturdy","count":1},{"word":"brick","count":1},{"word":"houses","count":1},{"word":"replacing","count":1},{"word":"humble","count":1},{"word":"thatched","count":1},{"word":"cottages","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"stood","count":1},{"word":"empty","count":1},{"word":"wasteland","count":1},{"word":"noticed","count":1},{"word":"calendar","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"shock","count":1},{"word":"grabbed","count":1},{"word":"passerby","count":1},{"word":"urgently","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"excuse","count":1},{"word":"current","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"answer","count":1},{"word":"legs","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"weak","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"changed","count":1},{"word":"loved","count":1},{"word":"ones","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"stranger","count":1},{"word":"fiction","count":1},{"word":"friend","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"detail","count":1},{"word":"based","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"events","count":1},{"word":"share","count":1},{"word":"legend","count":1},{"word":"deep","count":1},{"word":"within","count":1},{"word":"sacred","count":1},{"word":"peaks","count":1},{"word":"lies","count":1},{"word":"powerful","count":1},{"word":"immortality","count":1},{"word":"abode","count":1},{"word":"gathering","count":1},{"word":"spiritual","count":1},{"word":"energies","count":1},{"word":"heaven","count":1},{"word":"earth","count":1},{"word":"countless","count":1},{"word":"eons","count":1},{"word":"taken","count":1},{"word":"form","count":1},{"word":"majestic","count":1},{"word":"living","count":1},{"word":"mountains","count":1},{"word":"stretches","count":1},{"word":"surrounded","count":1},{"word":"fresh","count":1},{"word":"air","count":1},{"word":"nature's","count":1},{"word":"bounty","count":1},{"word":"add","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"one's","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"span","count":1},{"word":"starts","count":1},{"word":"game","count":1},{"word":"stumbled","count":1},{"word":"upon","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"secrets","count":1},{"word":"forgotten","count":1},{"word":"gather","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"lifetime","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"...The Weiqi pieces were scattered, but the guru remained calm. \"It's getting late,\" he said gently to the woodcutter. \"Shouldn't you be heading down the mountain?\"","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"As he glanced at the sky, the woodcutter was shocked to see how much time had passed. \"It couldn't have been more than two hours,\" he thought in disbelief. Feeling apologetic, he prepared to leave, worried that the guru would be annoyed with him.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"But when the woodcutter turned around, he nearly jumped out of his skin. The hermit guru, who had been playing Weiqi and drinking wine, was now gone. In his place lay a shattered Weiqi board and a heap of decaying bones.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"The woodcutter was so scared that he dropped his bamboo basket and ran down the mountain without even looking back.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"As he reached the mountain's base, he was hit with a stark realization. The quaint village he remembered had bloomed into a bustling town, with sturdy brick houses replacing the humble thatched cottages. And where his home once stood, only an empty wasteland remained.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"He noticed a date on the calendar that he had never seen before. In shock, he grabbed a passerby and urgently asked, \"Excuse me, can you tell me the current date and time?\"","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"As he heard the answer, his legs went weak. Everything had changed—time had passed and his loved ones were gone. No one remembered him anymore.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"...Well! That's the whole point. The truth is stranger than fiction, my friend. Every detail in that story is based on real events.","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"Let me share with you the other legend of Mt. Firmament, for deep within its sacred peaks lies a powerful secret... the \"Secret of Immortality\"!","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"We all know that Mt. Firmament is the abode of the Sentinel, gathering spiritual energies from both heaven and earth for countless eons. Over time, even the mountain itself has taken on the form of our majestic Sentinel!","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"Living in the mountains for long stretches of time, surrounded by fresh air and drinking from nature's own bounty, can add years to one's life span!","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"It all starts with that game of Weiqi, one that the woodcutter stumbled upon. Too bad those secrets have been long forgotten...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"Gather around now, people. You're in for the story of a lifetime...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035}]}